recursive-include skills *
recursive-include plugins *
recursive-include .claude-plugin *
recursive-include .agents *
recursive-include examples *
recursive-include assets *
include scripts/*.py
include README.md README.ko.md README.ja.md README.zh-CN.md README.zh-TW.md LICENSE CONTRIBUTING.md SECURITY.md CODE_OF_CONDUCT.md
